re from factset » description national bank of greece sa is a greecebased company which provides a range of financial services its financial services include retail and commercial banking asset management brokerage investment banking insurance and real estate at a global level the group operates in greece turkey the united kingdom south east europe see which includes bulgaria romania albania serbia and former yugoslavian republic of macedonia fyrom cyprus malta egypt and south africa the bank operates through the following business segments retail banking corporate and investment banking special asset unit sau global markets and asset management insurance international banking operations turkish banking operations as well as other that includes real estate management hotel and warehousing businesses more from reuters » officers and directors leonidas e fragkiadakis chief executive officer executive member of the board of directors age  dimitrios g dimopoulos deputy chief executive officer executive member of the board of directors age  paul k mylonas deputy chief executive officer executive member of the board of directors age  ioannis p kyriakopoulos group chief financial officer general manager age  nikolaos christodoulou general manager group coo age  panagiotis dasmanoglou general manager  group chief compliance officer and corporate governance officer secretary of board of directors and committees age  alexander benos general manager of group risk management chief risk officer cro age  georgios triantafillakis general manager of legal services age  petros fourtounis group human resources general manager age  georgios kaloritis general manager of internal audit of the bank and the group age  full list on reuters » google finance beta available in hong kong  canada  us  china  ukinformation is provided as is and solely for informational purposes not for trading purposes or advice and may be delayedto see all exchange delays please see disclaimer google  google ho